      <GoalText>Programming Kodu. (Step 1/3)</GoalText>
      <GamepadText>On row 2 move the pencil cursor to the plus sign next to WHEN then press &lt;a&gt; to add &lt;sensor.eyes&gt;</GamepadText>
      <MouseText>On row 2 click on the plus sign next to WHEN and add &lt;sensor.eyes&gt;</MouseText>
      <CompletionTest Name="Kode" Args="reflex 2 sensor.eyes" />
