      <Exclusion>None</Exclusion>
      <TargetModeGamepad>Programming</TargetModeGamepad>
      <TargetModeMouse>Programming</TargetModeMouse>
      <GoalText>Programming Kodu. (Step 2/3)</GoalText>
      <GamepadText>At the plus sign still on the WHEN side add &lt;filter.castle&gt;  The castle can be found in the objects group &lt;group.objects&gt;.
When done you should have WHEN &lt;sensor.eyes&gt;&lt;filter.fruit&gt;</GamepadText>
